item.title: What a Piece of Man Is Work
item.description: miss myself missing you - poliw.at [early release] 13:03 Freewrite #123089 ‘What a piece of work is man? Washing up dishes this morning plotting how to cut my dick off, I get too horny too often for this lifestyle. But it teaches patience, my current best reason to look forward to aging. Some men say it doesn’t go away. Well yeah that’s probably right, but you have more time to develop your interests.
